public class UngenerateReader
extends java.lang.Object

A reader class for ARC/INFO ungenerate files. Ungenerate files are ascii text files that are exported from arc/info. They have a very basic structure but for some reason remain popular with some data suppliers.

Author:
Ian Turton ian@geog.leeds.ac.uk
